{"tid":2397894,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"身體檢查選擇問題","createTime":"2021-02-06T20:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T02:22:05.000Z","uid":391465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"abdf667123cfd1c3d0c1b777abba37203aa5bb0f","tid":2397894,"uid":391465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T20:55:19.000Z","msg":"因為身邊陸續有人身體檢查搵到有問題，所以都打算去做個身體檢查去check吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網睇咗幾個懶人包都唔係好分到邊間好d，見到項目好似差唔多可以差成千蚊<br />\n個人筆直2000-2500左右，本身肥所以都知自己咩事，個報告唔會好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 努力減緊<br />\n主要想大概檢查下有冇咩病之類，應該唔洗做到好detail<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前自己睇咗幾間都好似唔錯<br />\n浸會醫院（標準）：見佢化驗項目幾多，可以check到肝功能個d幾吸引（覺得自己好大機會脂肪肝<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n聖德肋撒醫院（基本/晶緻）：同樣化驗項目幾多咁<br />\n香港體檢（基本/週末安心）：見佢價錢幾平但唔知同上面兩間醫院分別大唔大，上網冇咩評價<br />\n<br />\n本身冇做開身體檢查，唔係好識揀，想問吓大家意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55b618e65c7897639ecb7b10d900e2f5d501534","tid":2397894,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T22:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1434d078e6ed82cc17317ef8a7dd63f8a21b4b8f","tid":2397894,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T22:29:20.000Z","msg":"呢d睇你想檢查邊個器官炸喎<br />\n<br />\n冇標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03fee39f895f8d6df064dce4dfd3d35e40301297","tid":2397894,"uid":391465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1434d078e6ed82cc17317ef8a7dd63f8a21b4b8f","tid":2397894,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-0